title: Newly charming house short walk to the beach
posting_body: ['Charming house in the heart of the historic OB cottage district.', 'All original floors refinished, new kitchen cabinetry, plumbing, heating, newly refurbished bathroom, newly painted inside and out, all new appliances including w/d inside house.', 'Finalizing all revitalization including electrical upgrade.', 'The home features a one car detached garage that leads to a lovely back yard with many native plantings and your own personal veggie garden.', 'The covered patio is perfect for casual entertaining and family fun.', 'We would like to have tenants that maintain respect for your wonderful, sweet neighbors.', "The home is a short walk to the beach, coffee shops, farmer's market and all the wonderful eateries that make Ocean Beach its own unique little community.", 'If you are interested please send me your number.']
